snippet.title: The Construct
snippet.description:
A Platform to Become a ROS Developer from Zero

From robotics theory to ROS-based robot programming, we’ll help you master the concepts and tools you’ll need to become a ROS Developer.

Discover more ROS resources on our website: https://www.theconstructsim.com/.
